    <h1>Data Deletion Request - PeachPapaya</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> August 1, 2025</p>

    <div class="important">
      <p><strong>Your Right to Data Deletion</strong></p>
      <p>
        Under data protection laws, you have the right to request deletion of
        your personal information from our systems. We will process your request
        within 30 days.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>What Data We Store</h2>
    <p>We may store the following information about you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name and contact information</li>
      <li>Phone number and WhatsApp messages</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Payment information</li>
      <li>Lesson history and scheduling data</li>
      <li>Driver's license information</li>
      <li>Emergency contact details</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Request Data Deletion</h2>

    <div class="step">
      <h3>Option 1: Email Request</h3>
      <p><strong>Send an email to:</strong> sreerag@welovedinspace.studio</p>
      <p><strong>Subject line:</strong> "Data Deletion Request"</p>
      <p><strong>Include in your email:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your full name</li>
        <li>Phone number associated with your account</li>
        <li>Email address used for registration</li>
        <li>Reason for deletion (optional)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h3>Option 2: WhatsApp Request</h3>
      <p>If you have our WhatsApp number, you can send a message with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Request for data deletion</li>
        <li>Confirmation of your identity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>What Happens After Your Request</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Verification:</strong> We will verify your identity</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Processing:</strong> Your data will be deleted within 30 days
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Confirmation:</strong> You will receive confirmation of deletion
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Backup Removal:</strong> Data will be removed from all systems
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="warning">
      <p><strong>Important Notes:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deletion is permanent and cannot be undone</li>
        <li>You will lose access to your lesson history</li>
        <li>Any unused lesson credits will be forfeited</li>
        <li>We may retain certain records for legal compliance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Data Retention Exceptions</h2>
    <p>Some data may be retained for legal or regulatory purposes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Financial records for tax purposes</li>
      <li>Safety incident reports</li>
      <li>Insurance claim records</li>
      <li>Regulatory compliance data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> sreerag@welovedinspace.studio</p>
      <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 48 hours</p>
      <p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Up to 30 days</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Alternative: Data Access</h2>
